{
  "chapter": "049",
  "title": "外戚世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "自古以来受天命的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝王</span>以及承继大统、守成的君主，不只是因为他们自身德行茂盛，也确实有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">外戚</span>的辅助。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>朝的兴起得力于<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">涂山</span>氏，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>之所以被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">放</span>逐则是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">末喜</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>朝的兴起得力于<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有娀</span>氏，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>之所以被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>则是因为宠幸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妲己</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝的兴起得力于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姜原</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">大任</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">幽王</span>之所以被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">禽</span>获则是因为淫乱于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襃姒</span>。所以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">乾坤</span>为根基，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">关雎</span>开篇，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：书\">尚书（书）</span>赞美<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">釐降</span>，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>讥讽不亲自迎亲。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫妇</span>之间的关系，是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">人道</span>中最重要的伦常。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>的施用，唯独婚姻最为慎重。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乐</span>调和则<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四时</span>和顺，这是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">阴阳</span>变化、万物的纲纪。可不慎重吗？人能弘扬大道，但对于命又能怎样呢。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>匹之间的情爱太重大了，这种爱君主不能从臣下那里得到，父亲不能从儿子那里得到，何况低贱的人呢！即使欢合了，有的也不能生子；能生子了，有的又不能保全到最终：难道不是命吗？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>很少谈命，因为它难以言说。不通晓幽明变化之理，怎能认识性命之理呢？"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>以前的事已经粗疏简略了，其详情无从记载。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兴起后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕娥姁</span>成为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">正后</span>，儿子是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。等到晚年，她姿色衰退，宠爱减弱，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>得宠，她的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>几次几乎要取代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>驾崩后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span>灭<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">戚氏</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵王</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>后宫中只有那些不受宠、被疏远的才得以无恙。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>的长女是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宣平侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张敖</span>的妻子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张敖\">敖（张敖）</span>的女儿是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>因为亲上加亲的缘故，想方设法让她生子，始终没有生，就假称后宫别人的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人子</span>为自己所生。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>初定不久，继位的嗣君不明。于是尊贵外戚，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">王</span>诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>作为辅佐，并以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕禄</span>的女儿为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少帝</span>的皇后，想借此巩固根本到极点，然而并没有什么益处。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>驾崩，合葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕禄\">禄（吕禄）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕产\">产（吕产）</span>等人害怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，图谋作乱。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>们征讨他们，天意诱导其纲纪，终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">消灭</span>了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>。唯独留下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北宫</span>。迎接<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>即位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>，奉守<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>。这难道不是天意吗？若非<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>，谁能当此重任？"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>，父亲是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄氏</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时与原<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>宗室女子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏媪</span>私通，生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄</span>父在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山阴</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>了，就葬在那里。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>[叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏豹</span>[立为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏媪</span>就把她的女儿送入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏媪\">媪（魏媪）</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许负</span>那里看相，许负为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>相面，说她当生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>正与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>对峙，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>未定。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>当初和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>一起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，听到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许负</span>的话后，内心暗喜，于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">背</span>叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝[反叛，保持中立，进而与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>联合。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>等<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏王豹</span>，把他的国土设为郡，而把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>送到织室。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏豹\">豹（魏豹）</span>已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>进入织室，看见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>姿色动人，下诏收入后宫，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>却没有得到宠幸。起初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：薄姬\">姬（薄姬）</span>年少时，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管夫人</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵子兒</span>互相友好，约定说：\"谁先显贵，不要互相遗忘。\"不久<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管夫人</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵子兒</span>先得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>的宠幸。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>坐在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>宫的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋台</span>上，这两位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>相互笑谈<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>当初的约定。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>听见了，问其中缘故，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>把实情告诉了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>心中惨然，怜悯<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>，当天就召见并临幸了她。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>说：\"昨天夜里我梦见<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">苍龙</span>盘踞在我腹上。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"这是显贵的征兆，我替你成就它。\"一次临幸就生了男孩，这就是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>。此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>很少再见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>。"
    },
    "4.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>驾崩，那些曾经受宠幸的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姬</span>妾如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">戚夫人</span>之类，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>发怒，都把她们<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">幽</span>禁起来，不能出宫。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄姬</span>因为很少见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的缘故，得以出宫，跟随儿子到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>，做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄昭</span>也跟着去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>。"
    },
    "4.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>立为王<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>驾崩。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>议立新君，厌恶外戚<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>强横，都称赞<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄氏</span>仁爱善良，所以迎立<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文皇帝</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>改号称为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇太后</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄昭</span>被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">轵侯</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>的母亲也早先<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>了，葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎阳</span>以北。于是就追尊<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄</span>父为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">灵文侯</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽郡</span>设置园邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百家</span>，长丞以下的官吏守护陵墓，寝庙上食祭祀都按照<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>度。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎阳</span>以北也设置了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">灵文侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>园，规制如同<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">灵文侯</span>园。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>认为母亲家是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏王</span>的后裔，从小失去父母，其中奉养<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>诸<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>人出过力的，于是召集优待<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">魏氏</span>，根据亲疏赏赐。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄氏</span>封侯的共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。"
    },
    "4.6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>死在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>之后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>驾崩，葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南陵</span>。因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>合葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>，所以特地另起陵墓，靠近<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文皇帝</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span>。"
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕太后</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>以良家女子身份入宫侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>把宫人赏赐给诸王，每王<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五人</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>也在其中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>家在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河</span>，想去靠近家的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，请求主管<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>遣送的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宦者</span>吏说：\"请一定把我的名册放在去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的一组中。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宦者</span>忘记了，错把她的名册放入去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的一组中。名册上奏，诏书批准，就要出发。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>流泪哭泣，怨恨那<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宦者</span>，不想去，被强行催促，才勉强启程。到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>独独宠幸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>，生女儿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘嫖\">嫖（刘嫖）</span>，后来又生了两个男孩。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王后</span>生了四个男孩。先是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>未入京立为帝之前<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王后</span>就去世了。等到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>立为帝，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王后</span>所生的四个男孩相继病死。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数月（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>请求<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>的长子年龄最大，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦姬</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，女儿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘嫖\">嫖（刘嫖）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>。第<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>，不久又改封到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁孝王</span>。"
    },
    "5.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦皇后</span>的双亲早已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>，葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>下诏给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>，追尊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦后</span>的父亲为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安成侯</span>，母亲称为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">安成夫人</span>。命令<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河</span>设置园邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百家</span>，长丞奉守，比照<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灵文</span>园之<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦皇后</span>的兄长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>，弟弟叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦广国</span>，字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少君</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四五年</span>时，家里贫穷，被人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span>卖，家里不知道他下落。辗转了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀家</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>，给他的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>人进山烧<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">炭</span>，傍晚睡在山崖下的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>，山崖崩塌，全部压<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>了睡觉的人，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少君</span>得以脱身，没有<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>。自己占卜<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数天（时长）</span>当封侯，于是跟随他的主人到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦皇后</span>新<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>，家在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">观津</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">窦氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广国</span>离家时虽然小，但记得县名和姓氏，又曾经和姐姐一起采<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑</span>时跌下来，用这作为凭证，上书自陈身世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦皇后</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说起此事，召见他，问他，他详细讲了经过，果然是。又再问还有什么可作验证的。他回答说：\"姐姐离我西去时，和我在驿站的传舍中告别，讨来水为我洗头，请来食物给我吃，才离去。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦后</span>拉着他痛哭，眼泪横流。侍从左右都伏地哭泣，帮助<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>悲哀。于是厚赏田地、住宅、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span>，封赐族中兄弟，安家在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>。"
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌将军</span>等人说：\"我们的命将来系在这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>身上。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>出身低微，不能不替他们挑选<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">傅</span>师和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>，否则又要重蹈<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕氏</span>之事。\"于是就挑选有节行的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>士人与他们同住。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">少君</span>因此成为谦让的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>，不敢以尊贵骄人。"
    },
    "6.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦皇后</span>生病，失明。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>宠幸<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">慎夫人</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹姬</span>，她们都没有儿子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为帝，就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">广国</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">章武侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长君</span>先前<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>了，就封他的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：窦彭祖\">彭祖（窦彭祖）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南皮侯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">反</span>叛时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>的堂兄之子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦婴</span>，任侠好义，领兵立功，凭军功被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">魏其侯</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">窦氏</span>总共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>为侯。"
    },
    "6.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>喜好<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>之言，皇帝及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、诸位<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">窦</span>氏不得不读<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>，尊崇他们的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">术</span>。"
    },
    "6.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦太后</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>之后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>驾崩，合葬<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span>。遗诏把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东宫</span>所有的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span>财物赏赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长公主嫖</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槐里</span>人，母亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>，是从前<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>的孙女。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>嫁给<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槐里</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王仲</span>为妻，生一男叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>，还有两女。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王仲\">仲（王仲）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>改嫁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>的<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>，生了男孩<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田胜\">胜（田胜）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>的长女嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">金王孙</span>为妻，已生了一个女儿，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">卜筮</span>，卜者说两个女儿都当显贵。因此她想让两个女儿作不同凡响之人，就从<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">金氏</span>那里夺回长女。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">金氏</span>大怒，不肯与女儿决绝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>便把她送入<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>宫中。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>宠爱她，生了三个女儿一个男孩。男孩刚在胎里时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王美人</span>梦见<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日</span>进入她的怀中。她告诉了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>说：\"这是显贵的征兆。\"还没生，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>就驾崩了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>生下男孩。"
    },
    "7.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "先前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>又送她的小女儿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>入宫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>生了四个男孩。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>把<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">薄氏</span>女子选为他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为帝，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄皇后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>没有儿子，也不受宠。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>驾崩，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄皇后</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>的长子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荣</span>，他的母亲是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地人。[立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荣</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">长公主嫖</span>有个女儿，想嫁给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荣</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>嫉妒，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>的诸位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>都通过<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>面见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>，得到尊宠，都超过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>日益怨怒，谢绝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>，不答应。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>就想把女儿许给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>的儿子，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>答应了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>发怒，每天在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>面前说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>坏话：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>与各位贵<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>、受宠的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：薄姬\">姬（薄姬）</span>妾聚会时，常常让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侍者</span>向她们背后吐唾沫祝咒，怀着<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">邪媚道</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>因此对她怨恨。"
    },
    "9.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>曾经身体不适，心情不好，把那些为王的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">诸子</span>托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>，说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>之后，好好照顾他们。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>发怒，不肯答应，还说了无礼的话。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>怨恨，心中忌恨却没有发作。"
    },
    "9.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>每天称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>儿子的俊美，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>也认为他贤能，又想到以前所做的梦<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日</span>的征兆，但是还没有决定下来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>知道皇帝怨恨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>，趁着怒气未消，暗中派人催促<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>们奏请<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span>上奏完事后，说：\"'子以母贵，母以子贵'，如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的母亲没有名号，应当<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>发怒道：\"这岂是你该说的话！\"于是按律<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span>，并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，改封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临江王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>愈加怨恨，不得相见，因忧郁而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>。最终<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，她的儿子为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>的兄长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">盖侯</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "10.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>承袭称号为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>。尊<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇太后</span>的母亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧兒</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">武安侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田胜\">胜（田胜）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">周阳侯</span>。"
    },
    "10.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>有十三个男孩，一个为皇帝，十二个都为王。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>早<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>，她的四个儿子都为王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>的长女号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳公主</span>，次女为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">南宫公主</span>，再次为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">林虑公主</span>。"
    },
    "10.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">盖侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王信\">信（王信）</span>好饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田蚡</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田胜\">胜（田胜）</span>贪婪，善于文辞。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王仲</span>早<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>，葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">槐里</span>，追尊为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">共侯</span>，设置园邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百家</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平原君</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>，从<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田氏</span>葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>，设置园邑，规格比照<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">共侯</span>园。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景帝</span>之后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十六年（时长）</span>，在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元朔四年</span>驾崩，合葬<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>一家共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>为侯。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "11.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫皇后</span>字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>，出身低微。她家号称<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">卫氏</span>，出自<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span>的食邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>本是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>的歌女。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>刚即位时，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>没有儿子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>找来良家女子<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>，打扮安置在家中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸上</span>祓除归来，顺路经过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>家。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>让皇帝看那些侍立的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>都不喜欢。饮酒以后，歌女进来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>远远看去，只喜欢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>。当天<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>起身更衣，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>就在尚衣的车中侍候，得到宠幸。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>回到座位，非常高兴。赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>黄<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>就奏请把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>送入宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>拍着她的背说：\"去吧，好好吃饭，好自努力！一旦显贵，不要互相忘记。\"入宫<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，竟然没再受宠。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>挑选不适用的宫人，遣送出宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>得以见到皇帝，流泪请求出宫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>怜悯她，再次宠幸，于是怀了孕，恩宠日益隆盛。召她的兄长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫长君</span>、弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>。此后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子夫</span>非常受宠，恩宠不衰，共生了三女一男。男孩名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘据\">据（刘据）</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "12.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>时，娶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>的女儿为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span>。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为帝后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妃</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陈氏</span>，没有儿子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>能够成为嗣君，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大长公主</span>出了力，因此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈皇后</span>骄贵。听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>大受宠爱，怨恨，好几次几乎<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>愈加发怒。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈皇后</span>怀着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妇人</span>邪媚之术，事情渐渐被察觉，于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈皇后</span>，而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>。"
    },
    "12.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈皇后</span>的母亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大长公主</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>的姐姐，多次责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>的姐姐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳公主</span>说：\"皇帝没有我不得立为帝，已经后来又抛弃我的女儿，怎么如此不知感恩而背本忘恩呢！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳公主</span>说：\"是因为没有儿子的缘故才<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>的。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈皇后</span>为求子，花在医药上的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>共九千万，终究没有生子。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "13.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，在此之前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫长君</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>了，于是任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫青</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>立功，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长平侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>的三个儿子还在襁褓中，都封为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。以及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫皇后</span>所说的姐姐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫少兒</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫少兒\">少兒（卫少兒）</span>生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霍去病</span>，以军功封为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：霍去病\">冠军侯（霍去病）</span>，号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骠骑将军</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫青\">青（卫青）</span>号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>。<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫皇后</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘据\">据（刘据）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">卫氏</span>的旁支因军功发达，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五人</span>封侯。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫后</span>颜色衰退，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>地的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>得宠，生了儿子，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">齐王</span>。"
    },
    "14.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span>早<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李夫人</span>受宠，有一个男孩<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">昌邑王</span>。"
    },
    "14.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李夫人</span>早<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>，她的兄长<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李延年</span>以音律得宠，号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">协律</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">协律</span>，本是倡优。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>都因奸犯罪，被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>诛。当时他的长兄<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李广利\">广利（李广利）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">贰师将军</span>，在<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">大宛</span>，没有赶上<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>连，回来后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>已经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span>灭<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">李氏</span>，后来怜悯他家，就封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">海西侯</span>。"
    },
    "14.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "其他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姬</span>妾的儿子<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>，为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">广陵王</span>。他们的母亲不受宠，忧郁而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>。"
    },
    "14.5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李夫人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">卒</span>，就有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹婕妤</span>之类，更受宠爱。但她们都是以倡优出身而得见，不是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王侯</span>有土的士女，不可以匹配人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "15.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说：我担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官时，询问熟悉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>家旧事的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">锺离生</span>。他说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>在民间时所生的一个女儿，父亲是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">金王孙</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：金王孙\">王孙（金王孙）</span>已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>驾崩后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>已<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王太后</span>独守宫中。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王孙</span>名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩嫣\">嫣（韩嫣）</span>一向得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>宠幸，趁着机会对皇帝说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>有个女儿在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>说：\"为什么不早说！\"就派人先去看她，果然在她家。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>便亲自前去迎接她。清道戒严，先派遣旄骑出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">横城门</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span>车驾驰到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>。到小市西面的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">入里</span>，里门关闭，暴力开门，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span>直入里中，一直通到<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">金氏</span>门外停住，派武骑围住她家，担心她逃走，皇帝自己去而不得。就派左右<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>进去呼唤寻找她。家人惊恐，女儿逃匿到内室<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">床</span>下。搀扶着她出门，让她下拜谒见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>流泪说：\"唉！大姐，你藏得多深啊！\"下诏用副<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>载上她，回<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>飞驰回宫，直入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长乐宫</span>。命令在门上附上她的名籍，通报要谒见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说：\"皇帝累了，从哪里回来？\"皇帝说：\"刚才到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span>接到臣的姐姐，和她一起来的。\"又回头说：\"拜谒<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>！\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说：\"是那女孩吗？\"回答说：\"是的。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>为之流泪，女儿也伏地而哭。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>献上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>向前为她祝寿，奉上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千万</span>、奴婢<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百人</span>、公田<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百顷</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">甲第</span>，赐给姐姐。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>致谢道：\"让皇帝破费了。\"于是召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">南宫主</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">林虑主</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>一起来拜见姐姐，因此号为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">脩成君</span>。有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子男</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，女儿<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>。男子号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩成子仲</span>，女儿为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>的王后。这两个儿女不是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>骨肉，因此<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>怜爱他们。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩成子仲</span>骄纵恣肆，欺凌吏民，大家都以此为苦。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "16.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，皇后的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫青</span>字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲卿</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>身份被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长平侯</span>。有四个儿子，长子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卫伉\">伉（卫伉）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯世子</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯世子</span>常任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>，尊贵得宠。他的三个弟弟都封侯，各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千三百户</span>，一个叫<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">阴安侯</span>，另一个叫<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">发干侯</span>，第三个叫<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宜春侯</span>，贵震<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>歌谣唱道：\"生男不必喜，生女不必怒，难道没看见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫子夫</span>称霸<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>！\""
    },
    "16.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "这时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳主</span>寡居，应该找<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>匹配。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>和左右商议<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>城中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>可作丈夫的，都说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>可以。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>笑道：\"这人出身我家，过去常为我骑马出入，怎能做我的丈夫？\"左右<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侍御</span>说：\"如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>的姐姐是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，三个儿子都封侯，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>震动<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>为何轻视他呢？\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>就答应了。把这事告诉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>，命她禀告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>，于是下诏让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫将军</span>匹配<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平阳公主</span>。"
    },
    "16.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说：<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>如<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>变化。传说：\"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蛇</span>化为<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>，不变其纹；家族化为国，不变其姓。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>当时<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>，百恶<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭</span>除，光耀荣华，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>之时又何必牵挂呢！"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "17.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>时，宠幸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹婕妤</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">娙娥</span>，众人叫她\"娙何\"。娙何秩比<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中二千石</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">容华</span>秩比<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">婕妤</span>秩比<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。常有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">婕妤</span>升为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇后</span>的。"
    },
    "17.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹夫人</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>同时受宠，皇帝下诏不让她们相见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹夫人</span>自己向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>请求，希望能见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>一面，帝答应她。就让另一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>盛装打扮，随从仆御<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>，作为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>来见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹夫人</span>上前见她，说：\"这不是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>本人。\"帝说：\"凭什么这样说？\"她回答说：\"看她的身形体貌，不足以匹配人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>。\"于是帝便令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邢夫人</span>穿旧衣，独自前来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尹夫人</span>远远看见她，说：\"这才是真的。\"于是就低下头哭泣，自伤自己不如她。谚语说：\"美女入室，是恶女的仇家。\""
    },
    "17.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说：洗浴不一定要到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江海</span>，要紧的是能洗去污垢；<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>不一定要是<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">骐骥</span>，要紧的是善于奔跑；士人不必在世上有名，要紧的是知道；女子不必出身贵族，要紧的是贞洁美好。传说：\"女子无论美丑，入室都会被嫉妒；士人无论贤与不肖，入朝^朝见都会被嫉恨。\"美女是恶女的仇家。难道不是这样吗！"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "18.1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">钩弋夫人</span>姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">赵氏</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间</span>人。受到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>宠幸，生下一子<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>年七十时才生<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭帝</span>即位时，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>年龄。"
    },
    "18.2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卫太子</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>后，还没有重新<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">旦</span>上书，希望归国入宫宿卫。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>发怒，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北阙</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>刻<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了他的使者。"
    },
    "18.3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">上</span>居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘泉宫</span>，召画工图画<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>背负<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>的图像。于是左右<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>想<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>少子。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数天（时长）</span>，帝谴责<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">钩弋夫人</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>摘下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">簪珥</span>叩头。帝说：\"拉她下去，送<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">掖庭</span>狱！\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>回头看，帝说：\"快走，你不得<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">活</span>！\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云阳宫</span>。当时突然刮起暴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">风</span>扬起灰尘，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>为之感伤。使者夜里持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">棺</span>前往葬了她，做了标记。"
    },
    "18.4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "此后帝闲居时，问左右说：\"外面的人怎么议论？\"左右回答说：\"人们说，打算<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">立</span>她的儿子，为何要除掉他的母亲呢？\"帝说：\"是的。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">是非</span>是小孩愚人所能知道的吗？自古以来国家所以发生祸乱，是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>少而母亲壮年。女<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>独自居位则骄横，淫乱放恣，无人能禁。你没听说过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>吗？\"所以为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>生儿子的女子，无论男女，她们的母亲没有不被谴责而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>的，难道这不可以说是贤圣吗！这种高瞻远瞩，是为后世考虑的，绝非浅闻愚儒所能及。谥号为\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘武\">武（刘武）</span>\"，难道是虚名吗！"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：礼\">礼记（礼）</span>重视<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫妇</span>，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：易\">易经（易）</span>叙述<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">乾坤</span>。 阴阳相配成化，好比<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">月</span>处尊位。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河洲</span>降下淑女，天象垂示华轩。 德行彰显于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：大任\">任（大任）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：大姒\">姒（大姒）</span>，福庆流传于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：简狄\">娀（简狄）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姜嫄\">嫄（姜嫄）</span>。 到了我炎汉时代，此道依然存续。 <span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">吕</span>氏擅权于大宝，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">窦</span>氏喜好玄言。 自此以后，凭恩宠立嬖妾。 内廷无常<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主</span>，后嗣不繁衍。"
    }
  }
}